window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>I am a guardian. Born to protect, trained to fight, sworn to protect my charge.</i></p> <p>Once Alex discovers his charge in a high school theater class, he will do everything he can to keep her safe, whether it’s from teenage bullies or demonic forces fighting to destroy her. Will Cierra’s faith and Alex’s strength be enough to overpower terrifying events and evil powers or will it be too much for Cierra to survive?</p> <p>Guardian is a fast-paced paranormal urban fantasy book with closed-door romance, magic, power, demonic evil forces, and coming-of-age young adult themes. While it is a complete standalone story, it is also the first book in the Guardian trilogy. The next book is scheduled to release in December 2024 with the audiobook to follow.</p>"; 
